<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-19-0902 </DOCNO><TEXT>A general survey of the activities of the Dutch institution VEG-Gasinstituutin 1987 is given. The section on gas supply deals with: biogas, gas qualityand catalytic gas purification. With respect to gas distribution thefollowing items are discussed: effects of gas on plastics, physico-mechanicalbehavior of plastic pipelines, mechanics of pipelines, jointing methodsand characterization of materials. With regards to applications the authordiscusses: NO/sub x/ emissions, interchangeability of gases, heat pumps,effects of flue terminals on the performance of appliances, gas engines,catalytic combustion, thermo-chemical recovery, corrosion in condensingand conventional appliances and the use of plastics in flueing systems.19 figs.</TEXT></DOC>